Yodda Account and Data Deletion Policy

English Version

To delete your Yodda account and personal data:

Open the Yodda app.

Go to "Profile" → "Settings" → "Delete Account".

Confirm deletion.

Once confirmed, your account will be immediately disabled, and you will be logged out and unable to log in again.
All personal data (including your events, messages, and profile information) will become inaccessible and no longer visible to any users.

For security, integrity, and legal compliance purposes, certain non-identifiable records (such as anonymized logs) may be retained temporarily, but they are no longer linked to your identity and cannot be used to identify you.

If you need any help, please contact us at peterzikangwu@gmail.com
.

中文说明（附）

要删除您的 Yodda 账号及相关数据：

打开 Yodda 应用。

进入 “我的” → “设置” → “删除账号”。

确认删除后，您的账号会 立即被停用，并 无法再次登录。
所有个人数据（包括活动、消息、个人资料）将 立即不可访问、不再展示给任何用户。

出于安全、系统稳定性及合规要求，系统可能会临时保留部分匿名化记录，但这些数据 已与您的身份脱钩，无法再识别您的个人信息。

如需帮助，请联系 peterzikangwu@gmail.com
。
